## API Surface

### REST Endpoints

| Method | Path | Role | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/posts` | USER | Create post (→ PENDING_REVIEW) |
| POST | `/posts/:id/submit` | USER | Submit draft for review |
| POST | `/posts/:id/resubmit` | USER | Resubmit after revision |
| GET | `/moderation/queue` | MOD+ | Get pending posts |
| POST | `/moderation/moderate` | MOD+ | Approve/reject/revise |
| POST | `/moderation/lock/:postId` | MOD+ | Lock for review |
| DELETE | `/moderation/lock/:postId` | MOD+ | Release lock |
| GET | `/moderation/stats` | MOD+ | Queue statistics |

### tRPC Procedures

| Procedure | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `moderation.getQueue` | MOD+ | Pre-moderation queue |
| `moderation.moderate` | MOD+ | State-machine-validated action |
| `moderation.lockPost` | MOD+ | Exclusive review lock |
| `moderation.getQueueStats` | MOD+ | Dashboard stats |
| `moderation.forceUnlock` | ADMIN | Override lock release |
| `moderation.getSlaMetrics` | ADMIN | SLA monitoring |
| `admin.users.suspend` | ADMIN | Suspend user |
| `admin.users.assignRole` | ADMIN | Role management |
| `admin.auditLogs.query` | ADMIN | Paginated audit logs |
| `posts.submitForReview` | USER | Submit draft |
| `posts.resubmit` | USER | Resubmit post |
